  "time_ut": 1662042016,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is no change in the price of fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the fuel price formula, although the fuel price should be revised today (1), there will be no change in the fuel price, said Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy.",
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said that there is no possibility of fuel price revision according to the fuel price formula according to the imported cost of fuel and said that the price may be revised after the operations of the Sapugaskanda Oil Refinery are done as usual."
      ],
